# VibeCraft — Epic Fantasy Knight Fighter
#
# A heroic knight champion with dramatic proportions and
# intricate armor details. Designed for maximum visual impact.
#
# Dimensions  : ~2.2 units tall (with raised sword ~3.2)
# Poly count  : ~300 triangles
# Convention  : Y-up, right-handed coordinate system
#
# Features:
#   - Dramatic winged helm with tall crest
#   - Ornate gothic plate armor
#   - Massive flowing cape
#   - Imposing kite shield with heraldic design
#   - Legendary greatsword raised in victory pose
#   - Dynamic hero stance
#
# Material groups:
#   - Armor (polished steel)
#   - Gold trim (ornamental details)
#   - Cape (deep crimson)
#   - Leather (straps, grip)
#   - Steel blade (weapon)

mtllib fighter.mtl

# === TEXTURE COORDINATES =================================================
# UV mapping for materials

vt 0.0 0.0     # 1  bottom-left
vt 1.0 0.0     # 2  bottom-right
vt 1.0 1.0     # 3  top-right
vt 0.0 1.0     # 4  top-left
vt 0.5 0.0     # 5  bottom-center
vt 0.5 1.0     # 6  top-center
vt 0.5 0.5     # 7  center
vt 0.25 0.25   # 8  quarter
vt 0.75 0.25   # 9  three-quarter
vt 0.25 0.75   # 10 quarter-top
vt 0.75 0.75   # 11 three-quarter-top

# === NORMALS =============================================================

vn  0.0  1.0  0.0    # 1  up
vn  0.0 -1.0  0.0    # 2  down
vn  0.0  0.0  1.0    # 3  front
vn  0.0  0.0 -1.0    # 4  back
vn  1.0  0.0  0.0    # 5  right
vn -1.0  0.0  0.0    # 6  left
vn  0.707  0.707  0.0   # 7  up-right diagonal
vn -0.707  0.707  0.0   # 8  up-left diagonal
vn  0.0  0.707  0.707   # 9  up-front diagonal
vn  0.0  0.707 -0.707   # 10 up-back diagonal
vn  0.577  0.577  0.577 # 11 front-up-right
vn -0.577  0.577  0.577 # 12 front-up-left

